tool_description:
Detects  17 keypoints of a body.

The following are the keypoints. 
0: nose
1: left_eye
2: right_eye
3: left_ear
4: right_ear
5: left_shoulder
6: right_shoulder
7: left_elbow
8: right_elbow
9: left_wrist
10: right_wrist
11: left_hip
12: right_hip
13: left_knee
14: right_knee
15: left_ankle
16: right_ankle
name: Fast Pose Detection API
title: Fast Pose Detection API

api_list.name: Get PoseNet Predictions
api_list.description: Get PoseNet Prediction based on base64 input image
